hopobject.body: Could I take your name and number, please? ncs pharmacy wichita ks A sixth night of rioting in the southern Turkish city of Antakya, where a demonstrator died earlier this week after clashes with police. The district of Kadikoy in Istanbul also saw clashes after a peaceful protest march turned violent when it attempted to march on the local headquarters of the ruling AK party. Police charged at the crowd to disperse it, and tear gas and rubber bullets were fired.
